{
  "custom": {},
  "params": {
    "menuDockId": "config-file-menu",
    "closeMenuOnOutsideClick": true
  },
  "propConfig": {
    "params.menuDockId": {
      "paramDirection": "input",
      "persistent": true
    },
    "params.closeMenuOnOutsideClick": {
      "paramDirection": "input",
      "persistent": true
    }
  },
  "props": {
    "defaultSize": {
      "height": 900,
      "width": 1200
    }
  },
  "root": {
    "meta": {
      "name": "root"
    },
    "type": "ia.container.flex",
    "props": {
      "style": {
        "height": "100%",
        "classes": "cfm-page__root"
      }
    },
    "events": {
      "component": {
        "onStartup": {
          "config": {
            "script": "\texchange.cfm.runtime.sync_shell_session(self)\n"
          },
          "scope": "G",
          "type": "script"
        }
      },
      "dom": {
        "onClick": {
          "config": {
            "script": "\texchange.cfm.runtime.close_on_outside_click(self)\n"
          },
          "scope": "G",
          "type": "script"
        }
      }
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "meta": {
          "name": "PageWrapper"
        },
        "type": "ia.container.flex",
        "position": {
          "grow": 1
        },
        "props": {
          "direction": "column",
          "style": {
            "margin": "0 auto",
            "maxWidth": "1280px",
            "padding": "24px",
            "width": "100%"
          }
        },
        "children": [
          {
            "meta": {
              "name": "LandingCard"
            },
            "type": "ia.container.flex",
            "position": {
              "grow": 1
            },
            "props": {
              "direction": "column",
              "style": {
                "classes": "cfm-page__card"
              }
            },
            "children": [
              {
                "meta": {
                  "name": "LandingMarkdown"
                },
                "type": "ia.display.markdown",
                "position": {
                  "grow": 1
                },
                "props": {
                  "source": "# Config File Menu for Perspective\n\nThis project turns one YAML-lite or JSON menu configuration into a responsive Ignition Perspective navigation system.\n\n## Start Here\n\n- Open `/cfm/settings` for Settings, Help, Tag to Menu, Menu to Routes, and YAML to JSON tools.\n- Edit `Config File Menu/MenuContent.params.menuConfig` to define the menu tree.\n- Add Page Configuration routes for each menu `target`.\n- Use `/cfm/diagnostics` to review the bundled diagnostics dashboard during evaluation.\n\n## Dock Defaults\n\nThe standard layout starts open, pinned, and in push mode. Project-wide startup defaults live in the `exchange.cfm.runtime` project library script (`ensure_dock_defaults`).\n\n## Next Step\n\nFor a blank production site, import `config-file-menu-library.zip` first, then `config-file-menu-site.zip`. For a reference project with sample routes, import `config-file-menu-sample.zip` after the library.\n",
                  "style": {
                    "padding": "24px",
                    "fontSize": "15px",
                    "lineHeight": "1.5"
                  }
                }
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  }
}
